high_descs: Turn right and approach the sofa to your right.
Pick up the knife from the left end of the sofa.
Turn left from the sofa and go to the small coffee table against the wall just ahead.
Slice the loaf of bread on the coffee table.
Look towards the corner of the coffee table.
Place the knife down on the coffee table.
Look back towards the bread you just sliced.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Go left along the wall at the corner of the coffee table where you will see a white dining table ahead, go past that, then take a right and stop at the microwave on the right.
Use the microwave on the slice of bread and pick it back up.
Go back to the coffee table you sliced the bread on.
Place the bread slice down on the table next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of bread on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the sofa on the right.
Pick up a knife from the sofa.
Turn around and turn right to reach the coffee table.
Cut the bread on the coffee table with the knife.
Turn to face the coffee table.
Put the knife on the coffee table.
Turn to reach the coffee table to face the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the coffee table.
Turn left to reach the microwave on the right.
Heat the slice of bread in the microwave and take it out.
Head right and walk out of the kitchen and turn left to reach the coffee table.
Put the slice of bread on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of bread on the coffee table.
